{"article_id":"JYhaUCXhuBGMHdd1","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( CNN ) -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Sen. Marco Rubio , R-Florida , is laying out elements of his proposal","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"to reform the immigration system ,","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"which he pitches as much-needed modernization for the outdated system .","depth":3},{"id":4,"text":"Rubio ,","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"who was elected in 2010 to his first U.S. Senate term ,","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"told The Wall Street Journal in an interview","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"published Saturday","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"that his plan would include a permanent residency provision and a route to citizenship for those undocumented immigrants currently in the United States ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"but he stressed","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"that the plan was \" not blanket amnesty or a special pathway to citizenship . \"","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"The crux of his plan is to meet the country ' s economic needs ,","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"including expanding the skilled workforce and supporting agriculture ,","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"which has relied on undocumented immigrants .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"\" I do n't think","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"that in the 21st century we can continue to have an immigration system","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"where only 6.5 % of people","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"who come here ,","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"come here","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"based on labor and skill , \"","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"he said in the interview .","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"\" We have to move toward merit and skill-based immigration . ''","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"Rubio has previously spoken out in favor of immigration reform","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"and said","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"last summer","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"he was drafting a GOP alternative to the DREAM Act proposals ,","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"which would provide some form of legal status to young people","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"who were brought into the U.S. illegally","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"but who seek higher education or military service .","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"He put his plans on hold in June","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"as President Barack Obama announced","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"he would suspend deportations on many of these young adults .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"Critics dismissed it as a political move in an election year .","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"In a December interview on NBC , Obama said","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"he would work on immigration in the first year of his second term .","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"\" I 've said","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"that fixing our broken immigration system is a top priority .","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"I will introduce legislation in the first year","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"to get that done , \"","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"\" We can do it in a comprehensive way","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"that the American people support .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"That 's something","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"we should get done . \"","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"Rubio ' s proposal comes ahead of specifics from the president ,","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"whom","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"he says","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"has \" not done a thing \" on the issue .","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"Perhaps ,","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"he said ,","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"Obama would work with him on this issue","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"because \" maybe he 's interested in his legacy . \"","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"He supports increasing the caps for immigrants in both skilled and labor roles and allowing undocumented immigrants to \" earn \" a form of legal status .","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"He also supports an e-verify database system","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"which employers would be required to use","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"to determine","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"whether a potential hire is legally employable .","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"`` Here 's how I envision it , ''","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"he told the Journal .","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"`` They would have to come forward .","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"They would have to undergo a background check . ...","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"They would have to pay a fine ,","depth":16},{"id":62,"text":"pay back taxes ,","depth":17},{"id":63,"text":"maybe even do community service .","depth":17},{"id":64,"text":"They would have to prove","depth":17},{"id":65,"text":"they 've been here for an extended period of time .","depth":17},{"id":66,"text":"They understand some English","depth":17},{"id":67,"text":"and are assimilated .","depth":17},{"id":68,"text":"Then most of them would get legal status","depth":15},{"id":69,"text":"and be allowed to stay in this country . ''","depth":15},{"id":70,"text":"The system would not only crack down on illegal immigration ,","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"but he says","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"it would also benefit undocumented workers .","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"`` When someone is [ undocumented ]","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"they 're vulnerable to being exploited . ''","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"Besides being a solution to the immigration issue ,","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"Rubio says","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"it is politically beneficial to his party .","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"Obama won an overwhelming percentage of Latino and other minority voters .","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"`` The immigration issue is a gateway issue for Hispanics ,","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"no doubt about it , \"","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"\" No matter what your stance is on a number of other issues ,","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"if people somehow come to believe","depth":14},{"id":84,"text":"that you do n't like them","depth":15},{"id":85,"text":"or want them here ,","depth":15},{"id":86,"text":"it 's difficult to get them to listen to anything else . ''","depth":13}],"relations":[{"parent":173,"left":0,"right":172,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":172,"left":89,"right":171,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":89,"left":88,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":88,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":171,"left":106,"right":170,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":98,"right":105,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":95,"right":97,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":95,"left":93,"right":94,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":93,"left":90,"right":92,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":90,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":92,"left":91,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":91,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":97,"left":11,"right":96,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":96,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":104,"right":21,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":104,"left":103,"right":20,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":14,"right":102,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":102,"left":15,"right":101,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":100,"right":19,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":99,"right":18,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":99,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":170,"left":116,"right":169,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":116,"left":115,"right":32,"relation":"eval